# DTP_SPA_POC — Project Overview

## What This Project Is
DataTools Pro SPA — a Proof of Concept for the new Single Page Application front-end backed by a Laravel API. The repo is a **monorepo** with two primary surfaces:

1. **Laravel backend** at the repo root (`app/`, `routes/`, `database/`, etc.)
2. **React SPA** in the [`spa/`](mdc:spa) subdirectory

A third surface, **AI/Agentic workflows**, lives in [`ai/`](mdc:ai).

## Key Files & Directories

| Path | What it is |
|---|---|
| [`app/`](mdc:app) | Laravel application logic (controllers, models, services) |
| [`routes/`](mdc:routes) | Laravel HTTP + API routes |
| [`database/`](mdc:database) | Migrations, seeders, factories |
